  "description": "Combine arrows with potion effects and carry multiple effects in a single shot.",
  "body": "<div><div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif; font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT/MP_MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT_Header.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"2380\" height=\"874\"></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif; font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Multi Arrow Effects</strong> adds a new crafting mechanic that lets you merge up to three potion effects into a single arrow, unifying all their properties to create incredibly versatile and strategic projectiles.</span></p></div><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT/MP_MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT_Description.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"2382\" height=\"236\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\">This mod allows you to combine potion arrows and merge their properties into a single shot. You can stack up to 3 different potion effects on one arrow, creating powerful projectiles that apply multiple effects at once.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1396590/description_b5ceb87e-ed2f-456a-9c49-4403ed3be7dc.png\" width=\"368\" height=\"285\"></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\">All settings are fully configurable: you can adjust the maximum number of combined effects, tweak durations, block specific potions, or change crafting behavior directly from the config file, making the system fit any world or modpack.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\">It is fully compatible with other arrow and potion mods, allowing effects from any potion in the game. Potion arrows are created by surrounding a lingering potion with arrows, letting you apply any effect and later merge them into a single enhanced projectile.</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/null/description_eb7f55c5-3947-420b-89ff-328b3a283b3e.png\"></span></p></div>\n\n<div><p><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\"><strong>Want to play with friends?</strong></span></p><p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/thewizard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT/MP_MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT_Promo.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"2382\" height=\"353\"></strong></a></p><div><div><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\"><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/thewizard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>Get your own Minecraft server today</strong></a></span><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\"> and enjoy endless adventures with your friends! With top performance and reliable uptime, our servers guarantee a smooth and fun gaming experience for everyone. Use code <a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/thewizard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong>THEWIZARD</strong> </a>for a </span><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/thewizard\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: book antiqua, palatino, serif;\">25% discount!</span></strong></a></span></p><p><a href=\"https://discord.gg/FqhuAjYTGv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT/MP_MULTI_ARROW_EFFECT_Discord.webp\" width=\"2382\" height=\"235\"></span></a></p></div></div></div>",
